---
title: Mediterranean Chorizo, Halloumi & Couscous with Capsicum, Balsamic Rocket & Feta
description: Tonight’s pearl couscous is packed with smokey, comforting Mediterranean flavours like chorizo and capsicum. It’s hearty and cosy - all it needs is a sprinkle of crumbly feta to round out the perfect meal!
